Source:  Three Sheep and a Dog
Author:  GORDON
Vol / Page:  70
Edition:
Quote:  [A dog's] noise needs to be aimed directly at sheep which, the dog firmly believes, require its counselling and control. For this reason, we often talk about 'hunting the lead', though the dog is at the back of the mob.
